{"metadata": {"team_id": "necessarily", "topic_id": "1013", "run_id": "necessarily-engineering", "task": "english"}, "responses": [{"text": "This report addresses: Slow Food Movement", "citations": {}}, {"text": "Whenever I go to town to visit my family, I generally stop at these two spots if I am undecided where to dine at.", "citations": {"5e32bf70-91a5-4206-883d-a21d713bcd93_673021273": 8.0}}, {"text": "When I want something fresh and easy on the stomach, I generally go for vegetarian cuisine.", "citations": {"5e32bf70-91a5-4206-883d-a21d713bcd93_673021273": 7.0}}, {"text": "Many dishes share ingredients to make it easier to order food and cut down on food waste.", "citations": {"a7287cbc-9f8e-4dab-80fe-ca155a25ebad_1050830783": 6.0}}, {"text": "From smaller, more specialised menus to farm-to-table dishes, restaurant menus are promising to show some substantial changes.", "citations": {"a7287cbc-9f8e-4dab-80fe-ca155a25ebad_1050830783": 5.0}}, {"text": "Slow Table goes beyond the food, mindfully considering the key ingredients to creating a joyful gathering ambiance and pairing the dining experience in each box with sommelier selected wines, chic table decor, and music playlists -- all available at Slow-Table.com.", "citations": {"9c3cf9a6-88bd-4ebe-91d4-74ca8fbcb3b2_12882937": 9.0}}, {"text": "Slow Table Simplifies the Hosting Experience this Holiday Season with its All-New Approach to Gourmet Meal Kits\n\nFrom hosting to gift-giving, Slow Table's affordable-luxury food boxes are always appropriate.", "citations": {"9c3cf9a6-88bd-4ebe-91d4-74ca8fbcb3b2_12882937": 7.0}}], "references": ["5e32bf70-91a5-4206-883d-a21d713bcd93_673021273", "a7287cbc-9f8e-4dab-80fe-ca155a25ebad_1050830783", "9c3cf9a6-88bd-4ebe-91d4-74ca8fbcb3b2_12882937"]}
