{"metadata": {"team_id": "necessarily", "topic_id": "1017", "run_id": "necessarily-engineering", "task": "english"}, "responses": [{"text": "This report addresses: Live Action Disney Remakes", "citations": {}}, {"text": "In the realm of Disney's live-action remakes, whispers of a Hercules\u00a0adaptation have been circulating since 2020.", "citations": {"4a9091b3-af57-4bf2-b787-6f10c6a4c451_120168540": 13.0}}, {"text": "Enter Skyler, an industry insider, who dropped a bombshell: \"Not saying anyone should run with this as 100% fact but a name I hear Disney likes right now is Dua Lipa.\" This revelation, while tantalizing, should be taken with a grain of salt.", "citations": {"4a9091b3-af57-4bf2-b787-6f10c6a4c451_120168540": 10.0}}, {"text": "Skip to main content\n\nThe Little Mermaid lands on Disney Plus in September\n\nThe Little Mermaid lands on Disney Plus in September\n\n/\n\nYou can stream the live-action remake starting on September 6th.", "citations": {"e7523e4d-cef7-4868-b9ff-8953270fbcdf_489827103": 17.0}}, {"text": "As pointed out in The Verge\u2019s review of the film, Bailey delivered a strong performance as the titular mermaid that should appeal to new and old fans alike.", "citations": {"e7523e4d-cef7-4868-b9ff-8953270fbcdf_489827103": 13.0}}, {"text": "\u00d7\nYou will be redirected back to your article in seconds\n\nGuy Ritchie, who directed Disney\u2019s \u201cAladdin\u201d in 2019, is set to direct the upcoming live-action adaptation of the 1997 film \u201cHercules,\u201d Variety has confirmed.", "citations": {"d832a319-3dc5-415d-ae3a-2dec78804a6f_684061697": 14.0}}, {"text": "Tate Donovan voiced the lead role, alongside Susan Egan as his love interest, Megara, and James Woods as Hades, who kidnaps the demigod Hercules as a baby and forces him to live alongside mortals.", "citations": {"d832a319-3dc5-415d-ae3a-2dec78804a6f_684061697": 11.0}}], "references": ["4a9091b3-af57-4bf2-b787-6f10c6a4c451_120168540", "e7523e4d-cef7-4868-b9ff-8953270fbcdf_489827103", "d832a319-3dc5-415d-ae3a-2dec78804a6f_684061697"]}
